data.description: Located in the heart of Summerville, this 3 bedroom home showcases a welcoming family room with a fireplace that provides a cozy space for relaxation and gatherings. The home offers a separate dining area and converted garage. Outside you'll see a large fenced in backyard with a detached workshop/garage. this is a great home offering classic value and the kind of comforts you will be proud to call your own.
